MARION:
What a shame.

01:25.686 --> 01:29.316
<i>Arthur's gonna miss the
Halloween party and everything.</i>

01:29.423 --> 01:30.754
DOCTOR:
Get this prescription filled,

01:30.858 --> 01:32.553
have him take two every day.

01:32.660 --> 01:33.855
Will they help?

01:33.961 --> 01:35.122
